            <title>Dew v1.1.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's New in v1.1.0</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Timer sounds: Custom ticking and completion sounds</li>
                    <li>Volume control for timer audio</li>
                    <li>macOS menu bar integration</li>
                    <li>Fixed email confirmation auto-login</li>
                    <li>Fixed keyboard input in login forms</li>
                    <li>Fixed task reordering to maintain user arrangement</li>
                    <li>UI improvements for minimized timer state</li>
                </ul>
                
                <p><strong>System Requirements:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>macOS: macOS 10.15 or later</li>
                    <li>Windows: Windows 10 or later</li>
                </ul>
                
                <p><em>This update includes the latest features and improvements. The app will update automatically.</em></p>
            ]]></description>
